title: Aviceiro ou Fonte do Aviceiro
body: Location in the parish of Santo Antonio, a short distance from Lombo de D. Isabel, on the road leading to Curral das Freiras.

Santo Antonio: Parish located on the island of Madeira
Lombo de D. Isabel: Locality on the island of Madeira
Curral das Freiras: Locality on the island of Madeira
